import { Link } from "react-router-dom"
import styles from "./HeaderLinks.module.css"

function HeaderLinks({url, children}){
    return(
        <section>
            <Link to="./" className={styles.link}>
            HOME
            </Link>
        <Link to="./" className={styles.link}>
            HOME
        </Link>
        </section>
    )
}

export default HeaderLinks
